            <main class="card-content">
                <h2>Boarding Services</h2>
                <p>We understand that leaving your pet can be a stressful experience for both you and your furry friend. That's why we strive to make our boarding services a home away from home for your pet. Our facilities are designed to provide your pet with a comfortable and safe environment, and our staff is trained to cater to your pet's every need.</p>

                <p>Our boarding services include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Comfortable Accommodation**: Our spacious kennels are designed to make your pet feel at home. We provide comfortable bedding and plenty of room for your pet to move around.</li>
                    <li>**Nutritious Meals**: We provide healthy, balanced meals for your pet. If your pet has specific dietary requirements, we can accommodate those as well.</li>
                    <li>**Daily Exercise**: We ensure that your pet gets plenty of exercise. Our facilities include large outdoor play areas where your pet can run and play.</li>
                    <li>**Medical Care**: If your pet requires any medical attention during their stay, our on-site veterinarian is available to provide care.</li>
                </ul>
